    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "$46,900 - Exceptionally clean, well-kept mint-condition vehicle that presents about as well as you could hope for from a used car. The interior and exterior show extremely minimal wear, and it should stand out to buyers looking for a top-tier example rather than an average daily driver. Expect a vehicle that feels carefully maintained, shows beautifully, and is ready to enjoy immediately.",
