    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready to be put to work, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows clear cosmetic and age-related wear consistent with its condition, but it remains a practical choice for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone needing inexpensive wheels. Priced to sell and presented with straightforward value, this is a great opportunity to own a usable vehicle without stretching your budget.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable ride that could make a great starter car, backup vehicle, or little project for someone handy. It\u2019s priced with its condition in mind, and at this money there\u2019s a lot of value for somebody who wants straightforward transportation without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re realistic and want something inexpensive with potential, this could be well worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with good bones and a strong mechanical feel. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels composed for an older used car in this class. It shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but it presents as a usable, straightforward vehicle that can be driven and improved over time. Great candidate for someone who wants affordable transportation with enthusiast potential and room to make it their own.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap, tough, and ready to work. Not pretty, but it runs and gets the job done. Strong value for a budget buyer. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Turn the key and imagine the possibilities\u2014this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that tells a story before you even leave the driveway. It\u2019s an affordable entry into ownership for someone who appreciates a vehicle with personality, whether you need a practical around-town companion, a handy backup set of wheels, or a weekend project with real potential. The body carries the look of a machine that\u2019s lived a little, and that lived-in charm gives it a certain presence you just don\u2019t get from something anonymous. If you\u2019ve got a vision and enjoy bringing out the best in a car with spirit, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Practical, budget-friendly transportation with plenty of life left for the right owner. This vehicle shows its age but remains a solid opportunity for someone seeking inexpensive wheels, a project, or a dependable around-town driver. Straightforward value, easy entry price, and a chance to own for far less than newer alternatives.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    }
  ],
